@startuml
title EDF 景深扩展 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "EdfPanel" as Panel
participant "EdfService" as Service
participant "ProcessingQueue" as Queue
participant "ImageRegistration" as Registration
participant "EdfProcessor" as Processor
participant "ObservationSession" as Session
participant "ImageViewport" as View
participant "ProjectDocument" as Project

User -> Panel: 导入/选择 Z 轴图像序列
Panel -> Service: addSlice(frame, zIndex)
User -> Panel: 设置对齐和合成参数
Panel -> Service: createJob(stack)
Service --> Panel: ProcessingJob
Panel -> Queue: submit(job)
Queue -> Registration: align stack
Registration --> Queue: aligned ImageStack
Queue -> Processor: compose(stack)
Processor --> Queue: EdfResult
Queue -> Service: onCompleted(job)
Service -> Project: save stack refs, focus map and composite ref
Service -> Session: setDisplayFrame(compositeFrame)
Session -> View: setDisplayImage(compositeFrame)
View -> View: repaint EDF result + overlays

@enduml
